# RESNAV TEST
# Test resume navigation with PastCPA method
# Two aircraft on collision course at FL300

00:00:00.00>PAN -0.9 119.8
00:00:00.00>ASAS ON
00:00:00.00>RESO MVP
00:00:00.00>RESNAV PASTCPA

00:00:00.00>CRE GA001 B737 -0.900000,119.800000 0 FL300 200
00:00:00.00>CRECONFS GA002 B737 GA001 180 0 200 0 0 200 

00:00:00.00>ECHO Conflict between GA001 and GA002 - head on at FL300
